Order Granting Defendant's Motion to Modify Bond.
It is so ordered that the terms of bond shall be modified as follows:
1. Cash bail shall be amended from $2,000.00 cash to $1,000.00 cash; furthermore
2. upon cash bail being posted the Defendant is to go straight from custody to an in-patient
treatment facility; if there is not a facility available to accept the Defendant he is not to be
released;
3. the Defendant shall be transported from the jail to the treatment facility by the facility and
SHALL NOT transport himself to the treatment facility;
4. the defendant shall comply with all conditions set by the treatment facility;
5. all other non-monetary conditions will remain unchanged
